"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-04-fiance-wants-watch-olympics-phone-friends-wedding-21334408\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Weddingplanner and venue owner Alison Rios McCrone helps solve your dilemmas, no matter how big or small, in a weekly agony aunt column.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 31, \"end\": 37, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alison_DiLaurentis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8693135039270246e-29, \"text\": \"Alison\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alison_DiLaurentis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alison_DiLaurentis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your dilemmas\", \"from\": 63, \"to\": 76}, {\"ngram\": \"a weekly agony aunt column\", \"from\": 109, \"to\": 135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dear Alison, I hope you can settle a disagreement my fianc\\u00e9 and I are having.\", \"from\": 138, \"to\": 216, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a disagreement\", \"from\": 173, \"to\": 187}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are set to go to our friends' wedding next weekend, which we are really excited for - or at least I am.\", \"from\": 217, \"to\": 323, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our friends' wedding\", \"from\": 237, \"to\": 257}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My partner was, until he realised it would clash with his ability to watch theOlympics.\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 412, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My partner\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 335}, {\"ngram\": \"his ability\", \"from\": 379, \"to\": 390}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympics\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 411}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's pretty sports-mad and resents having to miss a moment of the action.\", \"from\": 414, \"to\": 487, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a moment\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 472}, {\"ngram\": \"the action\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 486}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He knows we have to go, so he's not dragging his feet on that.\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 550, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his feet\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 541}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is, however, planning on watching snippets of his favourite sports during the day on his phone.\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 649, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"snippets\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 596}, {\"ngram\": \"his favourite sports\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 620}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 635}, {\"ngram\": \"his phone\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I cannot believe it, it's so incredibly rude - and he just does not see why.\", \"from\": 651, \"to\": 727, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"rude\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 695}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Look, I can understand him checking the results every once in a while.\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 799, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the results\", \"from\": 765, \"to\": 776}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A quick glance at his phone can be explained.\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 845, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A quick glance\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 814}, {\"ngram\": \"his phone\", \"from\": 818, \"to\": 827}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But actually propping his phone up against a wine bottle and watching TV is disrespectful and embarrassing.\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 953, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his phone\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 877}, {\"ngram\": \"a wine bottle\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 902}, {\"ngram\": \"TV\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have heard friends previously complain about times they have seen people whip their phones out at weddings before to watch the football, and I just can not face them making similar comments about my fianc\\u00e9.\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 1163, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"friends\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 975}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1007}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1029}, {\"ngram\": \"their phones\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"weddings\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1063}, {\"ngram\": \"the football\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1092}, {\"ngram\": \"similar comments\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1146}, {\"ngram\": \"my fianc\\u00e9\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Can you please reassure me I am correct - and advise me on how I can make my partner realise what he's doing is wrong?\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1283, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my partner\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1249}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thanks, Miranda Weddings are joyful occasions - but they are also incredibly stressful.\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1294, \"end\": 1301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miranda_warning\", \"score\": 0.9999991899684216, \"rank\": 8.100223752533328e-07, \"text\": \"Miranda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miranda_warning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miranda_warning\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"joyful occasions\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1330}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether you are a bride or groom, best woman or man, family member or friend of the couple, the run up to the big day can be very tense.\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1511, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bride\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1398}, {\"ngram\": \"groom\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1407}, {\"ngram\": \"best woman\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1419}, {\"ngram\": \"man\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1426}, {\"ngram\": \"family member\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1441}, {\"ngram\": \"friend\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1451}, {\"ngram\": \"the couple\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1465}, {\"ngram\": \"the big day\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1492}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you need a bit of help with your quandary, Alison, who has run a venue for 10 years and helps couples plan weddings, is here to offer a helping hand.\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1665, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1559, \"end\": 1565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alison_DiLaurentis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8693135039270246e-29, \"text\": \"Alison\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alison_DiLaurentis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alison_DiLaurentis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1530}, {\"ngram\": \"help\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1538}, {\"ngram\": \"your quandary\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1557}, {\"ngram\": \"a venue\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1586}, {\"ngram\": \"10 years\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1599}, {\"ngram\": \"couples\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1617}, {\"ngram\": \"plan weddings\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1631}, {\"ngram\": \"a helping hand\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1664}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Emailplatform@metro.co.ukto share your issue anonymously with Alison and get it solved.\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1754, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1729, \"end\": 1735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alison_DiLaurentis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8693135039270246e-29, \"text\": \"Alison\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alison_DiLaurentis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alison_DiLaurentis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Emailplatform@metro.co.ukto\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1694}, {\"ngram\": \"your issue\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1711}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dear Miranda, I completely understand your frustration and concern.\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1824, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your frustration\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1810}, {\"ngram\": \"concern\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1822}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Weddings are significant events that require a lot of thought and effort by the happy couple, and your feelings about this matter are entirely valid.\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1974, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Weddings\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1833}, {\"ngram\": \"significant events\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1875}, {\"ngram\": \"thought\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 1886}, {\"ngram\": \"effort\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 1897}, {\"ngram\": \"the happy couple\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1917}, {\"ngram\": \"your feelings\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 1936}, {\"ngram\": \"this matter\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1954}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While we were hosting weddings duringthe Euros, some guests used the opportunity to watchthe footballduring thewedding mealor at random other times during the day, which made me think: what do the other guests at the table think when they are making small talk with everyone and one of the guests is sitting disengaged in those conversations and more engrossed in a match?\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 2348, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"weddings\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2006}, {\"ngram\": \"duringthe Euros\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2022}, {\"ngram\": \"some guests\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2035}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2056}, {\"ngram\": \"watchthe footballduring thewedding mealor\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2101}, {\"ngram\": \"random other times\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2123}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2138}, {\"ngram\": \"the other guests\", \"from\": 2169, \"to\": 2185}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 2189, \"to\": 2198}, {\"ngram\": \"small talk\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2236}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2250}, {\"ngram\": \"the guests\", \"from\": 2262, \"to\": 2272}, {\"ngram\": \"those conversations\", \"from\": 2298, \"to\": 2317}, {\"ngram\": \"a match\", \"from\": 2340, \"to\": 2347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This could have made the respective brides and grooms feel very disheartened and unsupported about their special day as those guests were not showing any interest in the wedding but more interested in watching football - so you are not alone.\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2592, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the respective brides\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2392}, {\"ngram\": \"grooms\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2403}, {\"ngram\": \"their special day\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2466}, {\"ngram\": \"those guests\", \"from\": 2470, \"to\": 2482}, {\"ngram\": \"any interest\", \"from\": 2500, \"to\": 2512}, {\"ngram\": \"the wedding\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2527}, {\"ngram\": \"football\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2568}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With that in mind, have a calm and honest conversation with your fianc\\u00e9.\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2666, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mind\", \"from\": 2607, \"to\": 2611}, {\"ngram\": \"a calm and honest conversation\", \"from\": 2618, \"to\": 2648}, {\"ngram\": \"your fianc\\u00e9\", \"from\": 2654, \"to\": 2665}]}, {\"sentence\": \"First, acknowledge his passion for sport and how much the Olympics means to him - then, explain why it is so important to you that he fully participates in the wedding without distractions.\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2857, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his passion\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2698}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2708}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2722, \"to\": 2734}, {\"ngram\": \"the wedding\", \"from\": 2824, \"to\": 2835}, {\"ngram\": \"distractions\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2856}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tell him your friends' wedding is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity and that you feel it is important for everyone to be present throughout the day.\", \"from\": 2859, \"to\": 3006, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your friends' wedding\", \"from\": 2868, \"to\": 2889}, {\"ngram\": \"a-lifetime\", \"from\": 2903, \"to\": 2913}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2964, \"to\": 2972}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 2998, \"to\": 3005}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is essential if you attend a wedding to support the happy couple - and you could even ask him how he would feel, if any of your guests were to watch sport at your upcoming wedding after you'd both put time and effort into making it the perfect day.\", \"from\": 3008, \"to\": 3259, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a wedding\", \"from\": 3038, \"to\": 3047}, {\"ngram\": \"the happy couple\", \"from\": 3059, \"to\": 3075}, {\"ngram\": \"your guests\", \"from\": 3134, \"to\": 3145}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 3160, \"to\": 3165}, {\"ngram\": \"your upcoming wedding\", \"from\": 3169, \"to\": 3190}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3212, \"to\": 3216}, {\"ngram\": \"effort\", \"from\": 3221, \"to\": 3227}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can also share your worries about the impression it might leave with your friends and how it could reflect on both of you.\", \"from\": 3261, \"to\": 3387, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your worries\", \"from\": 3280, \"to\": 3292}, {\"ngram\": \"the impression\", \"from\": 3299, \"to\": 3313}, {\"ngram\": \"your friends\", \"from\": 3334, \"to\": 3346}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let him know how uneasy the situation would make you feel and how embarrassing it would be if he constantly checked his phone in front of friends.\", \"from\": 3389, \"to\": 3535, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the situation\", \"from\": 3413, \"to\": 3426}, {\"ngram\": \"his phone\", \"from\": 3505, \"to\": 3514}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 3518, \"to\": 3523}, {\"ngram\": \"friends\", \"from\": 3527, \"to\": 3534}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This might change his view somewhat; but he will not know unless you tell him.\", \"from\": 3536, \"to\": 3614, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his view\", \"from\": 3554, \"to\": 3562}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Explain how you would prefer him to enjoy attending the wedding with you and socialising together without you feeling uncomfortable because of his desire to be distracted in front of friends.\", \"from\": 3616, \"to\": 3807, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wedding\", \"from\": 3668, \"to\": 3679}, {\"ngram\": \"his desire\", \"from\": 3759, \"to\": 3769}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 3790, \"to\": 3795}, {\"ngram\": \"friends\", \"from\": 3799, \"to\": 3806}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Encourage him to enjoy the wedding and catch up on the sports action later.\", \"from\": 3809, \"to\": 3884, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wedding\", \"from\": 3832, \"to\": 3843}, {\"ngram\": \"the sports action\", \"from\": 3860, \"to\": 3877}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This way, he can fully participate and be totally present during the wedding.\", \"from\": 3885, \"to\": 3962, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wedding\", \"from\": 3950, \"to\": 3961}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If he is unwilling to do that, ask him if he could discreetly catch up on results at less formal moments during the wedding -away from other guests to avoid drawing attention to himself.\", \"from\": 3964, \"to\": 4150, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"results\", \"from\": 4038, \"to\": 4045}, {\"ngram\": \"less formal moments\", \"from\": 4049, \"to\": 4068}, {\"ngram\": \"the wedding -away\", \"from\": 4076, \"to\": 4093}, {\"ngram\": \"other guests\", \"from\": 4099, \"to\": 4111}, {\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 4129, \"to\": 4138}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There will be moments during the day when he can check results or watch highlights during downtime - like during the drinks reception - but suggest that he does it in the loos if he needs to catch up.\", \"from\": 4152, \"to\": 4352, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"moments\", \"from\": 4166, \"to\": 4173}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 4181, \"to\": 4188}, {\"ngram\": \"results\", \"from\": 4207, \"to\": 4214}, {\"ngram\": \"highlights\", \"from\": 4224, \"to\": 4234}, {\"ngram\": \"the drinks reception\", \"from\": 4265, \"to\": 4285}, {\"ngram\": \"the loos\", \"from\": 4319, \"to\": 4327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once the wedding is over, he can properly take in the Olympics.\", \"from\": 4354, \"to\": 4417, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wedding\", \"from\": 4359, \"to\": 4370}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4404, \"to\": 4416}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If he has not checked the results throughout the day, watching them on-demand television will be more enjoyable.\", \"from\": 4418, \"to\": 4530, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the results\", \"from\": 4440, \"to\": 4451}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 4463, \"to\": 4470}, {\"ngram\": \"demand\", \"from\": 4489, \"to\": 4495}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Finally, remind him of how important it is to fully support your friends on their special day and to be respectful and attentive - because that's the main thing.\", \"from\": 4532, \"to\": 4693, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your friends\", \"from\": 4592, \"to\": 4604}, {\"ngram\": \"their special day\", \"from\": 4608, \"to\": 4625}, {\"ngram\": \"the main thing\", \"from\": 4678, \"to\": 4692}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ultimately, your approach should be about finding a balance that respects both his passion and the importance of the wedding.\", \"from\": 4695, \"to\": 4820, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your approach\", \"from\": 4707, \"to\": 4720}, {\"ngram\": \"a balance\", \"from\": 4745, \"to\": 4754}, {\"ngram\": \"both his passion\", \"from\": 4769, \"to\": 4785}, {\"ngram\": \"the importance\", \"from\": 4790, \"to\": 4804}, {\"ngram\": \"the wedding\", \"from\": 4808, \"to\": 4819}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you come to this with understanding and a willingness to find common ground, hopefully, your fianc\\u00e9 will see the importance of being attentive on such a special day.\", \"from\": 4822, \"to\": 4990, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"understanding\", \"from\": 4847, \"to\": 4860}, {\"ngram\": \"a willingness\", \"from\": 4865, \"to\": 4878}, {\"ngram\": \"common ground\", \"from\": 4887, \"to\": 4900}, {\"ngram\": \"your fianc\\u00e9\", \"from\": 4913, \"to\": 4924}, {\"ngram\": \"the importance\", \"from\": 4934, \"to\": 4948}, {\"ngram\": \"such a special day\", \"from\": 4971, \"to\": 4989}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Best wishes Alison Do you have a story you'd like to share?\", \"from\": 4992, \"to\": 5053, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5005, \"end\": 5011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alison_DiLaurentis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8693135039270246e-29, \"text\": \"Alison\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alison_DiLaurentis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alison_DiLaurentis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a story\", \"from\": 5023, \"to\": 5030}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Get in touch by emailingjess.austin@metro.co.uk.\", \"from\": 5054, \"to\": 5102, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"touch\", \"from\": 5061, \"to\": 5066}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Share your views in the comments below.\", \"from\": 5104, \"to\": 5143, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your views\", \"from\": 5110, \"to\": 5120}, {\"ngram\": \"the comments\", \"from\": 5124, \"to\": 5136}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Shelly-Ann Fraser-Pryce posts emotional statement after shock Olympics 100m withdrawal ArrowMORE:Olympics schedule and results: Noah Lyles claims gold for USA in men's 100m final ArrowMORE:Injured Olympic athlete gets carried off court by her opponent to huge ovation from crowd\", \"from\": 5145, \"to\": 5435, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5155, \"end\": 5178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly-Ann_Fraser-Pryce\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shelly-Ann Fraser-Pryce\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly-Ann_Fraser-Pryce\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly-Ann_Fraser-Pryce\"}, {\"begin\": 5284, \"end\": 5294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 5311, \"end\": 5314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9996825755735405, \"rank\": 0.0003172557864941661, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"emotional statement\", \"from\": 5185, \"to\": 5204}, {\"ngram\": \"shock Olympics\", \"from\": 5211, \"to\": 5225}, {\"ngram\": \"m withdrawal ArrowMORE\", \"from\": 5229, \"to\": 5251}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics schedule\", \"from\": 5252, \"to\": 5269}, {\"ngram\": \"results\", \"from\": 5274, \"to\": 5281}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 5301, \"to\": 5305}, {\"ngram\": \"men's 100m final ArrowMORE\", \"from\": 5317, \"to\": 5343}, {\"ngram\": \"Injured Olympic athlete\", \"from\": 5344, \"to\": 5367}, {\"ngram\": \"court\", \"from\": 5385, \"to\": 5390}, {\"ngram\": \"her opponent\", \"from\": 5394, \"to\": 5406}, {\"ngram\": \"huge ovation\", \"from\": 5410, \"to\": 5422}, {\"ngram\": \"crowd\", \"from\": 5428, \"to\": 5433}]}]}"